  "title": "Principal | Preschool Education",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Direct the comprehensive management of the center’s day-to-day functions.</li>\n  <li>Provide professional Early Childhood expertise, leadership and ensure consistent deliverance of quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Foster teachers in creating a positive and inviting learning environment.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all staff uphold strict health, safety, and cleanliness standards.</li>\n  <li>Prioritize the well-being of children by enforcing consistent safety and hygiene measures within the preschool</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate flexibility in working both autonomously and collaboratively within a team environment</li>\n  <li>Maintain open, constructive communication with parents and staff.</li>\n  <li>Review and improve the centre’s policies, philosophy, and procedures.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree and/or Diploma in Early Childhood (Leadership)/Advanced Diploma in Early Childhood Leadership (ADECL)</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant supervisory experience in a pre-school</li>\n  <li>Experience in leading and managing the team in SPARK Accreditation process</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out www.abercare.sg for more details</p>\n<p>Interested applicants may send in your resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
